&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Business and Sales Development Representatives who have 2+ years of outbound outreach experience. Experience with high volume cold calling and emailing is required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable talking to high level executives on the phone&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrate a high degree of diligence and accountability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An aptitude for research and discovery&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Core Competencies&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
