&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What’s the role?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Senior Data Platform Engineer, you’ll be a hands-on engineer on a small, high-ownership data team. You’ll work across the full data platform - relational, warehouse, and lakehouse systems - building and operating the pipelines that power compliance, analytics, and reporting workloads.&lt;/p&gt;
