&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and build pipelines that move data across systems - supporting data lake ingestion, compliance workloads, and cross-domain data flows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own pipeline operations end to end: monitoring, incident resolution, data quality, and documentation that lets any team member respond independently&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify technical debt and reliability risks and raise them with clear context and proposed next steps&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Success looks like: Pipelines run reliably. Known failure modes get fixed rather than worked around. You flag problems early and follow through on fixes.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
